    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specimen, powered by the legendary S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift throws, while the chassis has been vetted with a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. Recent maintenance includes a meticulous valve lash adjustment and a cooling system overhaul to maintain thermal efficiency during high-load scenarios. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, ensuring the high-lateral grip and communicative steering geometry the M-division is known for. While displaying the honest patina of a driven machine, the mechanical vitals remain stout and track-ready.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
