    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between luxury and daily utility, presenting in well-maintained condition. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and strictly smoke-free. The premium upholstery remains supple, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and heated seats, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth power, backed by a comprehensive service history. We have recently completed a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-ready. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is a solid, honest car that looks great and drives even better.",
      "price": 32500.0,
